Privacy Policy
We at editpad.org care about the privacy of the data being shared with us by our users that
                            is why are dedicated to protecting our client's privacy. This Privacy Policy aims to provide
                            our consumers with proper knowledge regarding what information
                            we collect and why, as well as how we utilize that information. All the way through this
                            policy, know that when we write "editpad.org" or "we" or "us", it means that we speak of
                            editpad.org, Inc., a corporation, and our subsidiaries
                            and other affiliates.
This Privacy Policy has been compiled to serve users who are concerned about how their
                            'Personally Identifiable Information (PII)' can be used online. As per US privacy law and
                            information security, PII is information that may be used on its own or
                            with other information to identify, locate, or contact an individual. We recommend you to
                            read the policy carefully to get a clear understanding of how we collect, use, or handle
                            your PII according to our Site, Software, App, and Services.
